Can be used to simulate mouse and keyboard actions, Can be used to handle pop-ups and also helps us in uploading files

Methods under robot class
Keypress() -- eg: robot.keyPress(KeyEvent.VK_DOWN)
KeyRelease() -- eg: robot.keyRelease(KeyEvent.VK_DOWN)
MousePress()-- eg: robot.MousePress(InputEvent.VK_DOWN)
MouseRelease()-- eg: robot.mouserelease(InputEvent.VK_DOWN)
MouseMove() -- eg: robot.mousemove(point.getX(),point.gety())

Limitations:
1. Mouse or keyboard event will only work on the current instance of the window
2. It is difficult to switch among different frames or window
3. MOuseMOve() depends on the screen resolution.
